10 REM BLINK LED D2 FIVE TIMES (HARDWARE ONLY - LED IS AT 0xFF0000)
20 REM ON REAL COR24 HW OR cor24-emu, THIS TOGGLES THE LED.
30 REM UNDER pv24t THE POKE TRAPS BECAUSE 16711680 IS OUT OF VM MEM.
40 FOR I=1 TO 5
50 POKE 16711680,0
60 PRINT "ON"
70 POKE 16711680,1
80 PRINT "OFF"
90 NEXT
99 END
RUN
BYE
